"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"Centcom says it hit 90 Iranian targets in the latest round of strikes. The Iranian health ministry says 14 people were killed since Tuesday. There is a decline in the number of ships, many carrying oil and gas, going through the waterway after attacks this week.\",            \"english_title\": \"Centcom Strikes Iranian Targets\",            \"translated_version\": \"Centcom dice que golpe\u00f3 90 objetivos iran\u00edes en los \u00faltimos ataques. El ministerio de salud de Ir\u00e1n dice que 14 personas murieron desde el martes. Hay menos barcos, muchos con petr\u00f3leo y gas, pasando por el agua despu\u00e9s de los ataques esta semana.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Centcom Ataca Objetivos Iran\u00edes\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"A video of the police interview with Tyler Robinson's roommate was played in court. This is part of a hearing to decide if the case will go to trial.\",            \"english_title\": \"Court Plays Roommate Interview\",            \"translated_version\": \"Un video de la entrevista de la polic\u00eda con el compa\u00f1ero de cuarto de Tyler Robinson fue mostrado en la corte. Esto es parte de una audiencia para decidir si el caso ir\u00e1 a juicio.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Corte Muestra Entrevista de Compa\u00f1ero\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"A former US Olympian canoeist denies accusations that he damaged the lining of the Lincoln Memorial Reflecting Pool. This decision came after a woman accused him of sexual assault, which he says is false.\",            \"english_title\": \"Olympian Denies Damaging Pool\",            \"translated_version\": \"Un ex cano\u00edsta ol\u00edmpico de EE.UU. niega acusaciones de que da\u00f1\u00f3 la piscina del Lincoln Memorial. Esta decisi\u00f3n vino despu\u00e9s de que una mujer lo acus\u00f3 de asalto sexual, lo cual \u00e9l dice que es falso.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ol\u00edmpico Niega Da\u00f1ar Piscina\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The runway is closed after a jet reportedly landed without using its landing gear and then caught fire.\",            \"english_title\": \"Runway Closed After Jet Fire\",            \"translated_version\": \"La pista est\u00e1 cerrada despu\u00e9s de que un avi\u00f3n aterriz\u00f3 sin usar su tren de aterrizaje y luego se incendi\u00f3.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Pista Cerrada Tras Incendio de Avi\u00f3n\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The attacks seem to be part of Ukraine's effort to cut off supplies and routes into and out of occupied Crimea.\",            \"english_title\": \"Ukraine Targets Crimea Supplies\",            \"translated_version\": \"Los ataques parecen ser parte del esfuerzo de Ucrania para cortar suministros y rutas hacia y desde Crimea ocupada.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ucrania Ataca Suministros de Crimea\"        }    ]}"